videos.description: Michigans' Muhammad-Ali Abdur-Rahkman gets the steal and finds Moritz Wagner for the 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Michigans' steal leads to Wagner 3-   pointer

videos.description: Wisconsin's Ethan Happ gets the steal and dunks it home on the fast break.
videos.headline: Wisconsin's Happ gets the steal and slams it home

videos.description: Wisconsin's D'Mitrik Trice gets the steal and scores the layup.
videos.headline: Wisconsin opens 2nd half scoring off a steal and layup

videos.description: Michigans' Moritz Wagner blocks the shot and it leads to D.J. Wilson's dunk on the nice feed from Zak Irvin.
videos.headline: Michigan's Irvin with the great pass to Wilson for the dunk

videos.description: Michigans' Zak Irvin banks in the 3-pointer just ahead of the shot clock
videos.headline: Michigans' Irvin banks in 3-pointer to beat the shot clock

videos.description: Michigan's Derrick Walton Jr drives and finds Muhammad-Ali Abdur-Rahkman in the corner for the 3-pointer plus the foul.
videos.headline: Michigan's Ali drains the 3-pointer and gets fouled

videos.description: Zak Irvin does a great job of staying inbounds and finds Moritz Wagner for the layup.
videos.headline: Irvin tip toes the sideline and finds Wagner for the layup

videos.description: Michigan gets the steal and Muhammad-Ali Abdur-Rahkman finds Mortiz Wagner for the big dunk.
videos.headline: Michigan steal leads to Wagner dunk

videos.description: Zak Irvin breaks down his big game with Jim Calhoun and Rece Davis in victory over Wisconsin.
videos.headline: Michigan's Zak Irvin breaks down his big game in victory

videos.description: Michigan uses a 9-0 run in the middle of the second half to pull away from No. 11 Wisconsin en route to a 64-58 victory.
videos.headline: Michigan tops Wisconsin at home
